3.7.4 Movemail Usage Summary
----------------------------

     movemail [OPTION...] INBOX DESTFILE [REMOTE-PASSWORD]

   The first argument, INBOX, is the url (see URL (*Editor's note:
dangling link*) ) of the source mailbox.  The second argument,
DESTFILE, traditionally means destination file, i.e. the UNIX mailbox
to copy messages to.  However, mailutils `movemail' extends the meaning
of this parameter.  You may actually specify any valid URL as DESTFILE
