`-L DIRNAME'
`--lib-dir DIRNAME'
     Set sieve library directory name

`-d LEVEL'
`--debug LEVEL'
     Set debugging level

   The Scheme programs produced by `sieve.scm' can be used with `guimb'
or `maidag'.


